to [Changes and New Works License](#changes-and-new-works-license).

## Distribution License

The licensor grants you an additional copyright license to
distribute copies of the software.  However, you may only
distribute unmodified copies of the software, and only for
[Noncommercial Purposes](#noncommercial-purposes).

## Changes and New Works License

The licensor grants you an additional copyright license to
make changes and new works based on the software.  However,
